   <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-association1-java-L10\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"10\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-association1-java-LC10\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">    <span class=\"pl-c1\">this</span><span class=\"pl-k\">.</span>a<span class=\"pl-k\">.</span>sumMethod();</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-association1-java-L11\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"11\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-association1-java-LC11\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  }</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-association1-java-L12\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"12\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-association1-java-LC12\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">}</td>\n      </tr>\n</table>\n\n\n  </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"gist-meta\">\n        <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/ppzxc/743aea5912549cde2714ca2989500d39/raw/a48630a67d142e922abfc847c16e9b8675858684/association1.java\" style=\"float:right\">view raw</a>\n        <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/ppzxc/743aea5912549cde2714ca2989500d39#file-association1-java\">association1.java</a>\n        hosted with &#10084; by <a href=\"https://github.com\">GitHub</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n</div></p>\n<ul>\n<li>B와 A는 연관이 있다.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 346px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b092894ae48a9159cdbc0cd5672f8806/1b082/association.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 28.61271676300578%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/b092894ae48a9159cdbc0cd5672f8806/4f75a/association.webp 346w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 346px) 100vw, 346px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/b092894ae48a9159cdbc0cd5672f8806/1b082/association.jpg 346w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 346px) 100vw, 346px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/b092894ae48a9159cdbc0cd5672f8806/1b082/association.jpg\"\n            alt=\"association.JPG\"\n            title=\"association.JPG\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">association.JPG</figcaption>\n  </figure></li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>연관 관계에서 중요하게 볼점은 <code>연관 관계의 방향</code>과 <code>멀티 플리시티</code>이다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>양방향 연관관계란, 서로의 존재를 알고 있다는 뜻이다. A와 B는 서로의 참조 값을 가지고 있다.\n단방향 연관관계란, 한쪽은 다른 한쪽의 존재를 모른다. A만 B의 참조 값을 가지고 있다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<h1>Dependency 의존 관계</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>dependency 예제</li>\n</ul>\n<p><div id=\"gist88671267\" class=\"gist\">\n    <div class=\"gist-file\">\n      <div class=\"gist-data\">\n        <div class=\"js-gist-file-update-container js-task-list-container file-box\">\n  <div id=\"file-dependency1-java\" class=\"file my-2\">\n    \n\n  <div itemprop=\"text\" class=\"Box-body p-0 blob-wrapper data type-java  \">\n      \n<table class=\"highlight tab-size js-file-line-container\" data-tab-size=\"8\" data-paste-markdown-skip>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-L1\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"1\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-LC1\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\"><span class=\"pl-k\">class</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">A</span> { }</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-L2\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"2\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-LC2\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">\n</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-L3\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"3\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-LC3\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\"><span class=\"pl-k\">class</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">B</span> {</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-L4\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"4\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-LC4\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  <span class=\"pl-smi\">A</span> a;</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-L5\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"5\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-LC5\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-L6\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"6\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-LC6\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  <span class=\"pl-c1\">B</span>() { }</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-L7\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"7\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-LC7\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-L8\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"8\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-LC8\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  public void method(<span class=\"pl-smi\">A</span> a) {</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-L9\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"9\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-LC9\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">    a <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">new</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">A</span>();</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-L10\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"10\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-LC10\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">    <span class=\"pl-c\"><span class=\"pl-c\">//</span> method의실행이끝나면참조없어짐</span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-L11\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"11\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-LC11\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  }</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-L12\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"12\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-dependency1-java-LC12\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">}</td>\n      </tr>\n</table>\n\n\n  </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"gist-meta\">\n        <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/ppzxc/743aea5912549cde2714ca2989500d39/raw/a48630a67d142e922abfc847c16e9b8675858684/dependency1.java\" style=\"float:right\">view raw</a>\n        <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/ppzxc/743aea5912549cde2714ca2989500d39#file-dependency1-java\">dependency1.java</a>\n        hosted with &#10084; by <a href=\"https://github.com\">GitHub</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n</div></p>\n<ul>\n<li>B가 A에게 의존한다.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 345px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2cdbb840e35c68877ce62a321873b85e/52bea/dependency1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 27.82608695652174%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/2cdbb840e35c68877ce62a321873b85e/923cb/dependency1.webp 345w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 345px) 100vw, 345px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/2cdbb840e35c68877ce62a321873b85e/52bea/dependency1.jpg 345w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 345px) 100vw, 345px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/2cdbb840e35c68877ce62a321873b85e/52bea/dependency1.jpg\"\n            alt=\"dependency1.JPG\"\n            title=\"dependency1.JPG\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">dependency1.JPG</figcaption>\n  </figure></li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>한 클래스의 메소드가 다른 클래스의 객체를 인자로 받아 그 메소드를 사용한다. (일반적인 경우)</li>\n<li>한 클래스의 메소드가 또 다른 클래스의 객체를 반환한다.</li>\n<li>다른 클래스의 메소드가 또 다른 클래스의 객체를 반환한다. 이때 이 메소드를 호출하여 반환되는 객체의 메소드를 사용한다.</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<h1>Association 연관 관계의 세부 구분</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>일반적인 연관 관계란 앞에서 살펴본 Association 연관 관계로 표현 된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Association 연관 관계의 특수 구분</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Association의 특수 구분은 Composition과 Aggregation의 특별한 형태로 구분 된다.</li>\n<li>특수 연관 관계의 구분은 <code>Life Cycle</code>이 같은지 다른지 이다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Aggregation 집합 연관</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>aggregation 예제</li>\n</ul>\n<p><div id=\"gist88671267\" class=\"gist\">\n    <div class=\"gist-file\">\n      <div class=\"gist-data\">\n        <div class=\"js-gist-file-update-con