a\" class=\"file my-2\">\n    \n\n  <div itemprop=\"text\" class=\"Box-body p-0 blob-wrapper data type-java  \">\n      \n<table class=\"highlight tab-size js-file-line-container\" data-tab-size=\"8\" data-paste-markdown-skip>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-interface-java-L1\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"1\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-interface-java-LC1\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\"><span class=\"pl-k\">interface</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">A</span> { }</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-interface-java-L2\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"2\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-interface-java-LC2\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\"><span class=\"pl-k\">class</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">B</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">implements</span> <span class=\"pl-e\">A</span> { }</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td id=\"file-interface-java-L3\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number\" data-line-number=\"3\"></td>\n        <td id=\"file-interface-java-LC3\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\"><span class=\"pl-k\">class</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">C</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">implements</span> <span class=\"pl-e\">A</span> { }</td>\n      </tr>\n</table>\n\n\n  </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"gist-meta\">\n        <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/ppzxc/743aea5912549cde2714ca2989500d39/raw/a48630a67d142e922abfc847c16e9b8675858684/interface.java\" style=\"float:right\">view raw</a>\n        <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/ppzxc/743aea5912549cde2714ca2989500d39#file-interface-java\">interface.java</a>\n        hosted with &#10084; by <a href=\"https://github.com\">GitHub</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n</div></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 302px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cf7971fc280315291d7f843caee9b80b/5b1bd/interface.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.17880794701986%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/cf7971fc280315291d7f843caee9b80b/794ea/interface.webp 302w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 302px) 100vw, 302px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/cf7971fc280315291d7f843caee9b80b/5b1bd/interface.jpg 302w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 302px) 100vw, 302px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/cf7971fc280315291d7f843caee9b80b/5b1bd/interface.jpg\"\n            alt=\"interface.JPG\"\n            title=\"interface.JPG\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">interface.JPG</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h1>끝으로</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>association 연관 관계의 특수 연관 관계인 aggregation과 composition의 관계 구분 법에서 재밌는 글을 봤다.\n<code>Life Cycle</code>을 구분하는 방법으로, 사람을 빗대어 표현했는데, 사람과 가같은 라이프 사이클인 팔과 다리 몸통 등 신체의 일부는 강한 집합 <code>Composition</code> 관계이고,\n부수적으로 착용하는 옷, 안경, 핸드폰 등은 연관 관계가 있지만 라이프 사이클이 다른 <code>Aggregation</code> 관계라는 것이다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1>Reference</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://geniusduck.tistory.com/entry/UML-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8%ED%8E%B8-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8-%ED%91%9C%EA%B8%B0-%ED%98%95%EC%8B%9D-%EB%B0%8F-%EA%B4%80%EA%B3%84%ED%91%9C%ED%98%84%EB%B2%95\">UML-기본편-기본-표기-형식-및-관계표현법</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://weicomes.tistory.com/179\">UML-기본 표기 형식 및 관계 표현법</a></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"date":"2018.03.29","slug":"/posts/UML기호정리","title":"UML 기호 정리"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/UML기호정리"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}